<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Projet Lydia</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      height: 100vh;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #0a0a0a 0%, #000000 100%);
      color:rgb(0, 255, 217);
      font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    /* Code qui défile en fond */
    .background-code {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      color: rgba(0, 255, 174, 0.05);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-family: monospace;
      animation: scroll 30s linear infinite;
      white-space: pre;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
    }

    @keyframes scroll {
      0% { transform: translateY(100%); }
      100% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
    }

    .typing-wrapper {
      display: inline-block;
      z-index: 2;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .line {
      font-size: 1.4em;
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-right: 2px solid #00ffae;
      width: 0;
      animation: typing 4s steps(60, end) forwards, blink 0.7s step-end infinite;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px #00ffae;
    }

    .line:nth-child(2) {
      animation-delay: 4.2s;
    }

    @keyframes typing {
      from { width: 0; }
      to { width: 100%; }
    }

    @keyframes blink {
      0%, 100% { border-color: transparent; }
      50% { border-color: #00ffae; }
    }

    .github-link {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #00c2aa;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform 0.3s, color 0.3s;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .github-link:hover {
      color: #00ffe1;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .footer {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 20px;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #008f6f;
      z-index: 2;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="background-code">
    Deploying... Initializing... Configuring Docker... Launching Apache... Ansible Playbook Running... ↵↵
    Deploying... Initializing... Configuring Docker... Launching Apache... Ansible Playbook Running... ↵↵
  </div>

  <div class="typing-wrapper">
    <div class="line">Automatisation du déploiement d’un serveur web Apache</div>
    <div class="line">via Docker et Ansible en environnement multi-distribution</div>
  </div>

  <a class="github-link" href="https://github.com/tonpseudo" target="_blank">Voir mon GitHub</a>
  <div class="footer">by Lydia</div>
</body>
</html>
